Package ExtendibleHashingScheme

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bucket
    This class represents the concept Bucket from Extendible Hashing.
    DataFile
    This class represents a file in the OS which is divided into many blocks.
    Directory
    This class represents the Directory Structure of the Extendible Hashing Scheme.
    DirectoryRecord
    The DirectoryRecord represents the HashMap used to map the global hash value to it's corresponding Bucket.
    SortBitString
    The helper class to provide the sortBuckets method with a comparator method.
    Utils
    This class has static methods that are used as helper functions and don't belong to any specific class.
